# CTDS Workforce Management System

## Overview

A Workforce Management System developed for managing employees, attendance, leave requests, tasks, KPI monitoring, and notifications.

## Features

### Employee Module
- Dashboard
- Attendance
- Leave Requests
- Task Tracking
- KPI Monitoring
- Notifications

### Admin Module
- User Management
- Attendance Monitoring
- Leave Approval
- Task Assignment
- Analytics Dashboard

## Technology Stack

### Frontend
- React
- Vite
- Tailwind CSS
- Shadcn UI

### Tools
- Git
- GitHub
- Antigravity IDE

## Installation

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
